data.description:
The location of this fabulous end unit condo can’t be beat! Overlooking the park, and walking distance to shopping, restaurants and Town Center activities 
situates this home in the perfect place. Ground level access and an attached 
two car garage are huge benefits! There is a relaxing courtyard providing 
wonderful outdoor living space. As you enter this super clean home, take note of the nine foot ceilings, arched doorways, big windows and sunny disposition. The great room is graced with mocha laminate wood flooring, a cozy gas fireplace, TV niche and ceiling fan. You’ll find plenty of room in the kitchen featuring lots of oak cabinets, low maintenance counter-tops, new GE stainless-like appliances and tile floors. A dining area is tucked nicely in the bay window. Casual dining is a snap at the breakfast bar. The chef will love the huge walk-in pantry. A spacious office is accented with archways, and is perfect for working at home. An expansive main floor laundry room includes the washer and dryer. A half bath is just steps away. Upstairs is host to a generous Junior suite and a marvelous Master suite! A mini loft area is great for an office nook.
Tile floors can be found in all bathrooms. Large closets abound! Upgraded carpet! This home is warm and inviting. With the HOA responsible for the exterior upkeep, you will have plenty of time to enjoy the nearby amenities including recreation centers, swimming pools, trails and more! 
Another "TESTA-monial"
